    <h2>Game Progress</h2>
    <p>Progress, rewards, cosmetics, and event content may change as the game is updated or balanced.</p>
    <h2>Availability</h2>
    <p>Some features, including ads, Game Center, analytics, and online events, may require network access or third-party services.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@neonninjarun.com">support@neonninjarun.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
